Available Tools: get_page_views | get_unique_visitors | get_session_duration | get_bounce_rate
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "url": "string", "from_date": "string", "to_date": "string", "granularity": "hourly|daily|weekly|monthly" }
Response Schema: { "url": "string", "period": "string", "views": number, "unique_visitors": number, "avg_session_seconds": number, "bounce_rate": number }
---
Question: What was the total traffic for the support portal during the software update window?
Call: { "func_call": "get_page_views", "url": "https://support.microsoft.com/windows", "from_date": "2023-11-14", "to_date": "2023-11-14", "granularity": "hourly" }
Response: { "url": "https://support.microsoft.com/windows", "period": "2023-11-14 to 2023-11-14", "views": 892000, "unique_visitors": 654000, "avg_session_seconds": 330, "bounce_rate": 0.29 }

Question: Can you show me the visitor count for the newsletter signup page last month?
